                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; name of the ruling king; incipits and headings of the texts; the text on fol. 16r is written alternately in red and black lines; directives for the ministers; some of the musical notation signs above the lines; abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
                     </handNote>
